NOTES:

  • This table may take upwards of 60 seconds to load, based on the speed (and memory) of your computer. Please be patient.
  • This table 99% complete. The Character Entity column is missing a few known entities, which I do plan on adding someday.
  • Characters 128-159 are Windows-1252 characters, and should not be used. Click on hyperlink for preferred entity.
  • New Greek, Math, and Symbol Entities were added on Friday, 6/23/06.
  • The full-range of Windows-1252 characters were added on Tuesday, 11/7/06.
  • UPDATE: Added a new "Non-standard Entity" column on Friday, 6/8/07. This column allows us to insert "homegrown" entities into the table.

Ryan Cartmill
